馬來西亞的人口是[[国家人口列表|世界第43位]]，領土是[[国家面积列表|世界第68位]]，人口3,170萬，土地面積329,847平方公里<ref name="CIA Fact Book" />。位于赤道北部，緯度介於[[北緯1度线|北緯1度线]]與[[北緯8度线|北緯8度线]]（有一小塊區域在1度以南），经度介于[[東經99度线|東經99度线]]與[[东经120度线|东经120度线]]之间。马来西亚主要由[[东马来西亚|東馬]]及[[西马来西亚|西馬]]（马来西亚半岛）组成，中间隔着[[南中国海|南中国海]]。陸地相接的邻国有西馬北部的[[泰国|泰国]]，以及東馬的[[汶莱|汶莱]]和[[印尼|印尼]]<ref name="CIA Fact Book" />。並與南方的[[新加坡|新加坡]]通過[[柔佛海峡|柔佛海峡]]相連接，領海鄰接[[越南|越南]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ugm.ac.id/en/?q=news/to-reduce-conflicts-indonesia-and-malaysia-should-meet-intensively |title=To Reduce Conflicts, Indonesia and Malaysia Should Meet Intensively |publisher=Ugm.ac.id |accessdate=2010-10-26 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101225091836/http://www.ugm.ac.id/en/?q=news%2Fto-reduce-conflicts-indonesia-and-malaysia-should-meet-intensively |archivedate=2010-12-25 }}</ref>與[[菲律賓|菲律賓]]<ref>{{cite web |author=The Earthtimes |url=http://www.earthtimes.org/articles/news/339542,gunboats-philippine-border-patrol.html |title=US donates four gunboats to Philippine border patrol |website=Earthtimes.org |date=2010-08-16 |accessdate=2010-10-17 |archive-date=2021-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120010253/http://www.earthtimes.org/articles/news/339542,gunboats-philippine-border-patrol.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。陸地邊界現在已清楚劃定，並大略依據地理特徵來界定，其中包括玻璃市河和哥樂河（Golok River）。马来西亚也对部分南海島嶼如[[弹丸礁|弹丸礁]]主张擁有主權，但海域疆界依然有待繼續協商<ref name="CIA Fact Book" />。馬來西亞是唯一在亞洲大陸與馬來群島都擁有領土的國家<ref name="Marshall" />，位於[[柔佛州|柔佛州]]南部[[笨珍县|笨珍县]]的[[丹绒比艾|丹绒比艾]]是亞洲大陸的最南端<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nst.com.my/Weekly/Travel/article/TravelTips/20050718145301/Article/index_html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070703124222/http://www.nst.com.my/Weekly/Travel/article/TravelTips/20050718145301/Article/index_html|archivedate=2007-07-03|title=Travel Times|publisher=Web.archive.org|date=2007-07-03|accessdate=2010-10-26|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.emedia.com.my/Weekly/TravelTimes/Friday/Frontpage/20030627112206/recent_article |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20030822193354/http://www.emedia.com.my/Weekly/TravelTimes/Friday/Frontpage/20030627112206/recent_article |archivedate=2003-08-22 |title=Travel Times |publisher=Web.archive.org |date=2003-08-22 |accessdate=2010-10-26 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。[[馬六甲海峽|馬六甲海峽]]位於[[蘇門答臘|蘇門答臘]]與[[马来西亚半岛|马来西亚半岛]]中間，是来往东西方的海運渠道<ref>{{cite news |author=Andrew Marshall |url=http://www.time.com/time/asia/2006/journey/strait.html |title=Waterway To the World – Summer Journey |publisher=Time.com |date=2006-07-31 |accessdate=2010-10-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060901014041/http://www.time.com/time/asia/2006/journey/strait.html |archivedate=2006-09-01 }}</ref>。

